    <h2 id="whatIs">What is composting?</h2>
    
    <p>Composting is the process of turning organic material (like food scraps and leaves) into soil. The soil produced from composting is extremely fertile. Composting can help reduce waste.  It is a useful way to rejuvenate soil.</p>

    <br>
    <br>
  
    <hr class="dashed">
  
    <h2 id="benefit">Benefits of Composting:</h2>
    <div class="container">
      <ul>
        <li>improving soil structure and health</li>
        <li>retain soil structure</li>
        <li>attract benefical organisms</li>
        <li>reduce soil erosion</li>
        <li>helps store carbon in the soil</li>
      </ul>

