    <h2 id="example">Composting Examples</h2>
   
    <p>You can compost with </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Food Scraps</li>
      <li>Grass Clippings</li>
      <li>Coffee grounds and paper filters</li>
      <li>Paper tea bags</li>
      <li>Eggshells (crushed)</li>
      <li>reduce soil erosion</li>
      <li>helps store carbon in the soil</li>
    </ul>

