    <h2 id="badExample">What Not to Compost:</h2>

    <p>You should AVOID composting with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Meat, fish and bones</li>
      <li>Cheese and dairy products</li>
      <li>Produce stickers</li>
      <li>Fats, oils and greases</li>
      <li>Glossy paper</li>
      <li>Dryer Lint</li>
    </ul>
  
